<% include ./partials/header.ejs %>
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <h1 class="text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        <br>
        <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-2">
            <h3>What is Lightbulb?</h3>
            <p>
                Lightbulb is an online web platform for sharing web and mobile app ideas among people around the world. 
                People can share their ideas by providing a title, photo and description. 
                Other people can comment and like the idea.
            </p>

            <h3>How do I Register?</h3>
            <p>
                In the upper right corner there is a link titled "Sign-up".
                To register, simply click on it and fill out the form.
            </p>

            <h3>How do I share an idea?</h3>
            <p>
                On the Lightbulb main page, there is a yellow button in the center titled "Share an Idea". 
                Click this button and fill out the form with your amazing idea!
            </p>

            <h3>How do I see my idea?</h3>
            <p>
                Click on your username located in the upper right corner. 
                After clicking, you will be redirected to your profile. 
                There you will be able to see all your ideas.
            </p>

            <h3>How do I like an idea?</h3>
            <p>
                On the idea page you will see a light bulb icon.. 
                To like the idea, just click once. To unlike the idea, click again.
            </p>

            <h3>How do I comment on an idea?</h3>
            <p>
                On the idea page, just below the description you will see a button titled "Add New Comment". 
                Click it to write your comment.
            </p>
            
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <h3>How do edit my idea?</h3>
            <p>
                On your idea page there will be a button called "Edit". Click it to open the edit form.
            </p>

            <h3>How do I delete my idea?</h3>
            <p>    
                On your idea page there will be a button called "Delete". Click it to permanently delete your idea.
            </p>
            <h3>How do edit my account?</h3>
            <p>
                On your user page there will be a button called "Edit". Click it to open the edit form.
            </p>

            <h3>How do I delete my account?</h3>
            <p>    
                On your user page there will be a button called "Delete". Click it to permanently delete your account.
            </p>

            <h3>What if I forgot my password?</h3>
            <p>    
                On the login page you will see a link titled "Forgot password?". 
                Click on it and enter your email in the form. 
                You will receive an email with the link to reset your password. 
                Click on it and enter your new password.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
